graph LR
    Notebooks["Notebooks-Downstream<br/>(Workbench Images)"]

    %% External Dependencies - Base Images
    Notebooks -->|base image| UBI9["UBI9 Python 3.11<br/>registry.access.redhat.com"]
    Notebooks -->|base image| UBI9_312["UBI9 Python 3.12<br/>registry.access.redhat.com"]
    Notebooks -->|base image (RStudio)| C9S["CentOS Stream 9<br/>Python 3.11"]

    %% External Dependencies - GPU
    Notebooks -->|GPU compute| CUDA["NVIDIA CUDA 12.6.3<br/>+ cuDNN 9.5 + NCCL 2.23.4"]
    Notebooks -->|AMD GPU| ROCm["AMD ROCm 6.2.4"]

    %% External Dependencies - IDE
    Notebooks -->|VS Code IDE| CodeServer["code-server 4.98.0"]
    Notebooks -->|R IDE| RStudio["RStudio Server<br/>2024.12.1-563"]
    Notebooks -->|reverse proxy| NGINX["NGINX 1.24"]

    %% External Dependencies - Tools
    Notebooks -->|CLI| OC["OpenShift CLI (oc)"]
    Notebooks -->|Python deps| Micropipenv["micropipenv"]
    Notebooks -->|PDF export| TexLive["TexLive"]
    Notebooks -->|document conversion| Pandoc["Pandoc"]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    NotebookController["ODH Notebook Controller"] -->|creates pods + sidecars| Notebooks
    Dashboard["RHOAI Dashboard"] -->|image selection UI| Notebooks
    Operator["rhods-operator"] -->|deploys ImageStreams| Notebooks
    Elyra["Elyra Pipeline Editor"] -->|runtime execution| Notebooks
    KFP["Kubeflow Pipelines"] -->|launches runtime pods| Notebooks

    %% External Services (runtime)
    Notebooks -->|oc CLI| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API"]
    Notebooks -->|pip install| PyPI["PyPI"]
    Notebooks -->|R packages| CRAN["CRAN"]
    Notebooks -->|data access| UserDB["User Databases<br/>(MongoDB/MSSQL/PostgreSQL)"]

    %% CI/CD
    Konflux["Konflux / Tekton"] -->|builds images| Notebooks
    Notebooks -->|publishes| Quay["quay.io/modh"]

